name: Voy Finance
additional_notices: No active trades are found for this coin. Please submit a ticket at %{link} if you think this is an error.

description.en:
We create ESG, financial and supply-chain solutions that accompany companies,
businesses, people, and the planet. Because we understand that without a planet, there is nothing to trade. We digitise banking trade finance and combine to the growing world of defi pools in a market that has a lack of real world assets to lend to enabling a real return on defi lending. Sustainable defi to RWAs connecting to banks and global trade.
